---
import CookieBanner from '../components/CookieBanner.astro';
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead
      title="Start Here — LongevityStack"
      description="New to LongevityStack? Start here. A guide to the evidence-based resources on sleep, supplementation, and cognitive performance."
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>

      <div class="page-header">
        <div class="tag">New here? Start with this.</div>
        <h1>Welcome to LongevityStack</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">This is a systems-engineering approach to human biology. Every article is built on peer-reviewed research — not trends, not influencer protocols.</p>
<div style="margin-top: 24px;">
  <a href="/blog/magnesium-glycinate-vs-threonate" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:var(--color-green);color:#EAF3DE;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;">Start here: Magnesium & sleep fundamentals (12 min) →</a>
</div>
      </div>

      <div class="author-card">
        <div class="avatar">BP</div>
        <div>
          <div class="author-name">Bernardo Paranhos</div>
          <div class="author-bio">Production Engineering student at UTFPR (Brazil), focused on systems optimization and applied analytics. I apply industrial systems thinking — bottleneck analysis, process optimization, failure mode identification — to the biology of sleep, supplementation, and cognitive longevity. <a href="/about">Full background →</a></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="divider-label">What this site is about</div>
<p style="font-size:15px;color:var(--color-muted);margin-bottom:28px;line-height:1.7;">Start with sleep. Then supplementation. Then cognition. Each pillar builds on the previous — sleep quality is the foundation that determines how well everything else works.</p>

      <!-- PILLARS -->
     <div class="pillars">
  <div class="pillar">
    <div class="pillar-icon" style="background:#EAF3DE">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path d="M12 3a6 6 0 0 0 9 9 9 9 0 1 1-9-9z" fill="#3B6D11"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h4>Sleep optimization</h4>
    <p>Temperature, light, timing and tracking protocols</p>
  </div>
  <div class="pillar">
    <div class="pillar-icon" style="background:#EAF3DE">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M9 3h6M10 3v6l-4 8a1 1 0 0 0 .9 1.5h10.2a1 1 0 0 0 .9-1.5l-4-8V3" stroke="#3B6D11" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
  <path d="M8.5 16.5h7" stroke="#3B6D11" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
</svg>
    </div>
    <h4>Supplementation</h4>
    <p>What the trials actually show — and what to skip</p>
  </div>
  <div class="pillar">
    <div class="pillar-icon" style="background:#E6F1FB">
      <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path d="M18.4961 10.7088L9.8603 19.5885C9.6207 19.8349 9.22228 19.5503 9.37764 19.2437L12.4518 13.1779C12.553 12.9783 12.408 12.7423 12.1842 12.7423H5.71762C5.45129 12.7423 5.31702 12.4211 5.5041 12.2315L13.5132 4.11699C13.7455 3.88157 14.132 4.14034 14.0029 4.44487L11.706 9.86069C11.6215 10.06 11.7694 10.2805 11.9859 10.2778L18.2773 10.1997C18.5444 10.1964 18.6823 10.5174 18.4961 10.7088Z" fill="#3B6D11"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h4>Cognitive performance</h4>
    <p>Focus, memory and long-term brain health</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="divider-label">Recommended reading order</div>

     <div class="reading-list">
        <a href="/blog/magnesium-glycinate-vs-threonate" class="reading-item">
          <div class="reading-num">01</div>
          <div class="reading-content">
            <div class="reading-tag">Supplements</div>
            <div class="reading-title">Magnesium Glycinate vs Threonate: Which Is Better for Sleep and Brain Function?</div>
            <div class="reading-meta">12 min · 8 RCT sources · The foundational article. Explains the blood-brain barrier bottleneck that determines which form you should take.</div>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog/engineering-of-sleep-18c-protocol" class="reading-item">
          <div class="reading-num">02</div>
          <div class="reading-content">
            <div class="reading-tag">Sleep</div>
            <div class="reading-title">Best Temperature for Sleep: Why 18°C (64°F) Improves Deep Sleep</div>
            <div class="reading-meta">14 min · 6 RCT sources · Why your bedroom temperature is the most underrated sleep variable — and the exact protocol to fix it.</div>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog/best-magnesium-for-sleep" class="reading-item">
          <div class="reading-num">03</div>
          <div class="reading-content">
            <div class="reading-tag">Supplements · Buyer guide</div>
            <div class="reading-title">Best Magnesium for Sleep: The Evidence-Based Guide (2026)</div>
            <div class="reading-meta">11 min · 7 RCT sources · If you want to buy magnesium and want to know exactly which form to get, start here.</div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="divider-label">How this site works</div>

      <div class="how-it-works">
        <div class="how-item">
          <div class="how-num">1</div>
          <div class="how-text">
            <strong>Every claim is sourced.</strong> Articles link directly to PubMed or NIH. If a study is weak, we say so. If the evidence is preliminary, we label it that way.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="how-item">
          <div class="how-num">2</div>
          <div class="how-text">
            <strong>Affiliate links are disclosed inline.</strong> Some links earn a commission. They are always labeled. Recommendations are not influenced by commission rates.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="how-item">
          <div class="how-num">3</div>
          <div class="how-text">
            <strong>This is not medical advice.</strong> See the <a href="/medical-disclaimer">Medical Disclaimer</a>. Use this site as a research starting point, not a replacement for professional guidance.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="how-item">
          <div class="how-num">4</div>
          <div class="how-text">
            <strong>Content is updated as evidence evolves.</strong> Publication dates and update dates are shown on every article.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="newsletter-box">
        <div class="nl-eyebrow">Free weekly digest</div>
        <div class="nl-title">Get the weekly LongevityStack deep dive.</div>
<div class="nl-sub">Evidence-based. No hype. No influencer noise. Used by engineering students and professionals optimizing performance.</div>
        <div class="nl-form">
          <input type="email" placeholder="your@email.com" />
          <button>Subscribe →</button>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:#5F5E5A;margin-top:10px;">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime. Join early readers of LongevityStack.</div>
      </div>

    </main>
    <CookieBanner />
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  main { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 28px 80px; }

  .reading-item * {
  text-decoration: none !important;
}

  .page-header { padding: 52px 0 36px; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--color-border); margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .tag { display: inline-block; background: var(--color-green-light); color: var(--color-green); font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; padding: 4px 14px; border-radius: 20px; margin-bottom: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  h1 { font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 34px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.6px; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .subtitle { font-size: 17px; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.75; }

  .author-card { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; background: var(--color-surface); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px 22px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .avatar { width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%; background: #C0DD97; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-green); flex-shrink: 0; }
  .author-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .author-bio { font-size: 13px; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.65; }
  .author-bio a { color: var(--color-green); font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none; }

  .divider-label { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 1.2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #B4B2A9; margin-bottom: 24px; padding-top: 8px; }

  .pillars { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 52px; }
@media(max-width: 640px) {
  .pillars { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  h1 { font-size: 26px; }
  .nl-form input { width: 100%; }
  .nl-form { flex-direction: column; }
}
  .pillar { background: #fff; border: 0.5px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 22px 18px; }
  .pillar-icon { width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%; margin-bottom: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 16px; }
  .pillar h3 { font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--color-text); }
  .pillar p { font-size: 12px; color: var(--color-hint); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .pillar-link { font-size: 12px; color: var(--color-green); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }

  .reading-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; margin-bottom: 52px; }
  .reading-item { display: flex; gap: 20px; padding: 22px 0; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--color-border); align-items: flex-start; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.15s; border-radius: 8px; padding-left: 8px; padding-right: 8px; }
.reading-item:hover { background: var(--color-surface); text-decoration: none; }
.reading-item:hover * { text-decoration: none !important; }
  .reading-item:first-child { border-top: 0.5px solid var(--color-border); }
  .reading-num { font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #D3D1C7; flex-shrink: 0; width: 36px; line-height: 1; }
  .reading-tag { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; color: var(--color-green); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .reading-title { font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text); text-decoration: none; line-height: 1.4; display: block; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .reading-title:hover { color: var(--color-green); }
  .reading-meta { font-size: 12px; color: var(--color-hint); line-height: 1.6; }

  .how-it-works { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 52px; }
  .how-item { display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start; }
  .how-num { width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--color-green-light); color: var(--color-green); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
  .how-text { font-size: 15px; color: var(--color-text); line-height: 1.7; }
  .how-text strong { font-weight: 600; }
  .how-text a { color: var(--color-green); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }

  .newsletter-box { background: #1a1a18; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px 32px; }
  .nl-eyebrow { font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.2px; color: var(--color-green-mid); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .nl-title { font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #FAFAF7; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .nl-sub { font-size: 12px; color: #888780; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .nl-form { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .nl-form input { background: #2a2a28; border: 0.5px solid #444441; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 14px; font-size: 13px; color: #FAFAF7; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; width: 220px; outline: none; }
  .nl-form button { background: var(--color-green-mid); color: #fff; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 8px; border: none; cursor: pointer; }
</style>